{
  "id": "12-3",
  "title": "Act 3: Parting Ways",
  "startNode": "main",
  "nodes": {
    "main": {
      "events": [
        {
          "type": "marker",
          "id": "ch12_act3_start"
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "blackout",
          "args": {
            "enabled": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeIn",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "When {{characters.soren.name}} left, {{characters.elias.name}} followed.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 14
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 600
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Not because he agreed—his face made that clear. But he followed because he knew the cost of letting {{characters.soren.name}} walk alone right now was harder to measure than following him. He needed to be there. He needed to watch. He needed to be present before this extreme reached the point of no return.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Before he left, he stood beside {{characters.lyra.name}} for a second without speaking. Then he followed {{characters.soren.name}}'s footsteps.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "ambient",
          "text": "Footsteps echoing in the corridor, then fading to silence.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} remained kneeling.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 10
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Outside the corridor, Solmaris's forces withdrew after completing this phase of their advance. The sound of tide receding—footsteps, mechanical sounds, and the sudden silence left behind when the resonance wave generators shut down. Silence like a blank canvas spreading over the ruins, covering them.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 12
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1000
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} waited until all those sounds had faded before standing.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 10
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "Around her: the Wasteland, the ruins, the fire-scorched ground, the pieces of destroyed Solmaris machinery, the electromagnetic baton with its dead battery, and air so still it seemed like nothing had ever happened here.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 10
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1200
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "She embraced that cold weight and fell. Fell into a place she had no words to describe. There was no sound there, no direction, nothing to hold onto. Only emptiness. Only cold. Only that dissipation she couldn't grip hard enough to keep.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 10
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The dissipation continued spreading with every second she held it tight, spreading and spreading, until she lost its boundaries, until she didn't know where that dissipation ended, or if it had an end at all.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 8
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "The Wasteland wind blew from afar, sending ash up, letting it fall.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 8
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 1500
        },
        {
          "type": "line",
          "layer": "narration",
          "text": "{{characters.lyra.name}} didn't move. She held that cold, broken shell, alone, in that silent space where nothing existed, falling, bottomless.",
          "reveal": {
            "mode": "typewriter",
            "cps": 8
          },
          "log": true
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 4000
        },
        {
          "type": "ui",
          "op": "fadeOut",
          "ms": 3000,
          "args": {
            "stay": true
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "wait",
          "ms": 800
        },
        {
          "type": "end"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "onComplete": [
    "reward",
    "complete"
  ]
}